1
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:23,720
It wasn't easy to return from Guixu alive.

2
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,040
We must return at once.

3
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:38,960
Are you Li Jing?

4
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:40,480
You are of the Sea Clan.

5
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:41,560
Clam Demon.

6
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:43,760
The Ninth Prince has orders.

7
00:00:43,760 --> 00:00:45,360
Any of the Human Race entering here

8
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:47,160
shall have their Primordial Spirit destroyed at once.

9
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:02,920
Impudent demon!

10
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:03,720
You court death!

11
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:10,440
Within the Mirage Pearl's illusion...

12
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,440
you will see your own Inner demons.

13
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:16,960
And your Primordial Spirit shall perish here.

14
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,840
I do not wish to kill you.

15
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:23,760
But I cannot defy the Ninth Prince's command.

16
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:24,960
So...

17
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,400
Apologies.

18
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,760
Father.

19
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,520
What is wrong, Father?

20
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,720
Master, please accept me.

21
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,360
Stop it!

22
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,480
Demon!

23
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:47,040
This power...

24
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,120
Ancient...

25
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,360
Powerful...

26
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,600
Scorching...

27
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,960
Could it be the Phoenix Clan?

28
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,360
Xuan Qi.

29
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,360
Your Highness.

30
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,360
Go.

31
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,800
Bring Si Meng to me.

32
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,680
Yes, sir.

33
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,360
It seems...

34
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,800
I must add another trump card.

35
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,240
There is a gate over there.

36
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,880
Good. Let's give chase.

37
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:39,880
This is the Five Great Avenues.

38
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,080
I'm back.

39
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,400
Li Jing has traveled through time too.

40
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,560
Mom!

41
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,080
Someone time-traveled!

42
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,920
Baby...

43
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,040
That's called cosplay.

44
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,080
Let's go.

45
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,400
I'll explain it to you later.

46
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,000
Mom, cosplay...

47
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,080
This...

48
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,880
This is time travel!

49
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,680
Catch them, quick!

50
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,640
Could it be...

51
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:22,440
this is the legendary Sword Flight?

52
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,080
Ah, yes.

53
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,160
It's a shared one.

54
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,480
What kind of spell is this?

55
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,480
We can't catch up!

56
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,400
Are we just going to let them get away?

57
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,520
Kid.

58
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,680
Are you in a hurry?

59
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,000
What?

60
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,520
They caught up in a taxi!

61
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,200
Focus on your Sword Flight.

62
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,520
Heavenly Thunder Spell!

63
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,320
My spell isn't working!

64
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,000
Don't worry.

65
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,880
I have a plan.

66
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,760
Why have we stopped moving?

67
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,520
Young lady.

68
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,400
I'm not a god, you know.

69
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,320
We're stuck in traffic.
